overview: Setlist: 1. No Enemiesz 2. Giant In My Heart (followed by dance routine to a mashup of Bell Biv DeVoe "Poison" and Rob Base "It Takes Two") 3. What Is Love (Haddaway cover) 4. Hallelujah (Leonard Cohen cover) 5. Losing My Mind 6. So Deep 7. Hideaway
title: Kiesza - Live at iTunes Festival 2014
